com.gams.api

Class GAMSParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gams.api.GAMSSymbol<GAMSParameterRecord>
      • com.gams.api.GAMSParameter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<GAMSParameterRecord>

    public class GAMSParameter
extends GAMSSymbol<GAMSParameterRecord>
    This is the representation of a parameter symbol in GAMS. It exists in a GAMSDatabase and contains GAMSParameterRecords which one can iterate through.
    See Also:
    GAMSDatabase, GAMSDatabase.addParameter(String, int), GAMSDatabase.addParameter(String, int, String), GAMSDatabase.addParameter(String, String, Object...)
